## SVG Generation

Use `generateCloudflareLogoSvg()` to get copy-paste ready SVG markup for non-Svelte contexts.

```ts
import { generateCloudflareLogoSvg } from "kumo-svelte/components/cloudflare-logo";
const glyphSvg = generateCloudflareLogoSvg({ variant: "glyph" });
const fullSvg = generateCloudflareLogoSvg({ variant: "full" });
const blackSvg = generateCloudflareLogoSvg({ color: "black" });

await navigator.clipboard.writeText(
  generateCloudflareLogoSvg({ variant: "glyph", color: "color" }),
);
```

## API Reference

### CloudflareLogo

Extends `SVGSVGElement` and accepts all standard SVG attributes.

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `variant` | `"glyph" \| "full"` | No | Logo variant. Defaults to `"full"`. |
| `color` | `"color" \| "black" \| "white"` | No | Color scheme. Defaults to `"color"`. |
| `class` | `string` | No | CSS classes for sizing, such as `w-36`. Height adjusts automatically. |

### PoweredByCloudflare

Extends `HTMLAnchorElement` and accepts all standard anchor attributes.

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `color` | `"color" \| "black" \| "white"` | No | Color scheme for the logo and text. Defaults to `"color"`. |
| `href` | `string` | No | Link destination. Defaults to `"https://www.cloudflare.com"`. |
| `target` | `string` | No | Link target. Defaults to `"_blank"`. |
| `rel` | `string` | No | Link relationship. Defaults to `"noopener noreferrer"`. |
| `class` | `string` | No | Additional classes merged with the badge styles. |

### generateCloudflareLogoSvg

Generates SVG markup as a string.

| Option | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `variant` | `"glyph" \| "full"` | No | SVG variant. Defaults to `"full"`. |
| `color` | `"color" \| "black" \| "white"` | No | SVG color scheme. Defaults to `"color"`. |
